data.description: Welcome home.  This beautiful house on a large lot is ready to welcome you!  Enjoy quiet, country living conveniently located outside the city limits of Waxahachie.  Upon entering you will feel right at home in the front living area which opens into the elegant formal dining.  With 2 living areas on the first floor, there is an abundance of room for any size family.  The kitchen boasts granite countertops, ample storage and a beautiful island while the laundry room with built in shelving and full size washer dryer connections maximizes the utility space.  Located on the 2nd floor is the over-sized primary suite with garden tub and walk-in closet. You will also find 3 more bedrooms and another full bathroom on the second floor.  The large backyard is perfect to grill and enjoy the evenings.
